HEADWORD: Titanous
<hw>Ti"tan*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Designating certain
compounds of titanium in which that element has a lower valence as
contrasted with <contr>titanic</contr> compounds.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

